WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:02.580
I'll tell you the truth. I want you to do me a favor.

2
00:00:02.840 --> 00:00:05.160
How many people from each of your Jiang family can help?

3
00:00:05.510 --> 00:00:08.400
First, you are not allowed to tell anyone that I am not sick.

4
00:00:08.760 --> 00:00:11.990
Second, there was a car accident in the Jiang family twenty years ago.

5
00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:15.510
I feel more and more now that there is something fishy about this car accident.

6
00:00:15.830 --> 00:00:17.290
Not like a night, like a person.

7
00:00:17.530 --> 00:00:19.810
I want you to help me find out who did it.

8
00:00:20.140 --> 00:00:21.000
Why should I help you?

9
00:00:21.330 --> 00:00:23.630
If you confiscate these, within two days,

10
00:00:23.870 --> 00:00:25.510
I will be kicked out of the Jiang family by my aunt and second uncle.

11
00:00:26.320 --> 00:00:28.360
But if you accept these,

12
00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:31.060
I will be kicked out of the Jiang family tonight.

13
00:00:31.060 --> 00:00:33.390
But you just took advantage of others

14
00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:36.030
Make others think you are someone who can be taken advantage of

15
00:00:36.820 --> 00:00:38.700
But I don’t have the heart to do those dark things

16
00:00:38.700 --> 00:00:40.260
I think you can help me

17
00:00:42.190 --> 00:00:42.750
You want me to help you?

18
00:00:50.430 --> 00:00:50.710
I have nothing to gain

19
00:00:50.710 --> 00:00:53.130
Just a broken stone

20
00:00:53.220 --> 00:00:54.400
No sincerity at all

21
00:00:54.400 --> 00:01:02.640
Start today

22
00:01:02.640 --> 00:01:05.970
You are the wife of Jiang Mian, the future heir of the Jiang family.

23
00:01:06.640 --> 00:01:09.450
No one in the entire Lingjiang clan dares to bully you.

24
00:01:12.740 --> 00:01:13.240
It’s a deal

25
00:01:13.240 --> 00:01:18.380
Now that we are legally married

26
00:01:18.380 --> 00:01:20.220
Otherwise, how about going through the process?

